text: Consolidated Annual Open Data Plans (Spatial Data Plans included)

value: DATA.GOV.HK is coordinated by the Digital Policy Office with the participation of different government departments and public / private organisations to disseminate various types of open data for free re-use for both commercial and non-commercial purposes subject to the Terms and Conditions of Use as published on DATA.GOV.HK and related websites.
